import React from 'react';
import { Col, Nav, Row, Tab } from 'react-bootstrap';


function Works() {
    return (
        <>
            <Tab.Container id="left-tabs-example" defaultActiveKey="second" >
                <Row className="bg-info justify-content-center" style={{width: "fit-content"}}>
                    <Col sm={2} >
                        <Nav variant="pills" className="flex-column">
                            <Nav.Item>
                                <Nav.Link eventKey="first">J. Willard Marriott Library</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                            <Nav.Item>
                                <Nav.Link eventKey="second">CodingAPE School</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav.Item>
                        </Nav>
                    </Col>
                    <Col sm={9}>
                        <Tab.Content>
                            <Tab.Pane eventKey="first">First tab content</Tab.Pane>
                            <Tab.Pane eventKey="second">Second tab content</Tab.Pane>
                        </Tab.Content>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Tab.Container>
        </>
    );
}



export default Works;
